Hair: ApachiiSkyHair-  http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?
Brows: Brows- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?
Eyes: TheEyesOfBeauty- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?

[color=#ff0000][size=4]Follow these steps:[/size][/color]

1. Download my mod and install it at data/skse/plugins/chargen/presets
2. Open Skyrim using SKSE
3. Load any working save file
4. Open the console
5. Type showracemenu
6. Select the BretonRace
7. Look for the slide option "preset slot"
8. Press F9 and done
